title: 50 Pieces - 27mm Piezo Disc Elements No Leads
features: Primarily used in acoustic guitars, CBGs, drums, stomp boxes, etc...
27mm brass outer diameter plate, 15mm Ceramic plate
description: Piezo discs are great for constructing pickups for acoustic instruments. Many users love them as the pickup in cigar box guitars, and they are a favorite amongst people experimenting with electric drum triggers. These 27mm discs are a medium size and work well in many applications! Resonant Frequency 4.6KHz. Resonant Resistance 250 ohm max. Capacitance 16,000pF
